Package: rfinancialriskshiny
Title: R Financial Risk Analysis and Visualization with Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gabriel", "Demetrios Lafis", email = "gabriel.lafis@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive package for financial risk analysis and visualization using Shiny.
    The package provides tools for Value at Risk (VaR) calculation, Expected Shortfall (ES),
    portfolio optimization, stress testing, Monte Carlo simulations, and risk factor analysis.
    Features include interactive dashboards, risk reports, and various risk visualization tools.
